Thomas B. Kin Chong -LRB- born May 24 , 1938 -RRB- is a Canadian-American comedian and actor , who is known for his marijuana-themed Cheech & Chong comedy albums and movies with Cheech Marin , as well as playing the character Leo on Fox 's That '70s Show .
He became a naturalized United States citizen in the late 1980s .